:

*Vremenom* je stigao do željenog cilja. (He eventually reached the desired goal.)

Kako je *vremenom* sve teže bilo, tako je njegov optimizam opadao. (As it got harder over time, his optimism was declining.)

Uspešno je preživeo *vremenom* ispitivanog bolesti. (He successfully survived the illness tested by time.)

Njegova obdarenost *vremenom* je postala poznata. (His giftedness over time became known.)

*Vremenom* je sve više učio o svetu oko sebe. (He was learning more and more about the world around him over time.)